/webui
*.exe

# Build
/dist/
/build/
/.gotmp/

# Go vendor directory (dependencies are managed via go.mod/go.sum, not vendoring)
# Notice: vendoring is useful for air-gapped environments. 
# If you need to vendor dependencies, you can run `go mod vendor` and commit the 
# resulting /vendor/ directory. However, by default, we ignore it.
/vendor/

